s=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">Your baby becomes more independent in their sleep routine, needing less assistance from you.<br \\/>\\r\\nBest-case scenario: Your baby can sleep on their own with minimal or no support (usually less than 5 minutes).<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6893\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"HEADLINE6888\\\">\\r\\n<h3>The Power of POH&rsquo;s Sleep Training Courses<\\/h3>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6888\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">Unlock the incredible benefits of our sleep training course and watch your baby thrive:<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"IMAGE6885\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-image ladi-transition\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-image-background\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6891\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">IMPROVED NIGHT SLEEP<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6892\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">Your baby&#39;s nighttime sleep becomes longer, minimizing disruptions during the day.<br \\/>\\r\\nBest-case scenario: Your baby sleeps 10-12 hours at night, waking up for feeding only 1-3 times and falling back to sleep immediately. Once your baby weighs over 6kg, they can sleep through the night for 10-12 hours without needing to eat.<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6896\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6897\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6893\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">TIME FOR YOU TO REST &amp; SELF-CARE<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6894\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">With your baby&#39;s improved sleep, you&#39;ll have valuable time to recharge and take care of yourself.<br \\/>\\r\\nRelax and unwind, knowing your baby is peacefully sleeping.<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6898\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6899\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH6889\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">BABY KNOWS HOW TO SELF-SOOTH<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6894\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6895\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6901\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"VIDEO6900\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-video\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-video-background\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE6900\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"BUTTON6906\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-button ladi-transition\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-button-background\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-button-headline ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"BUTTON_TEXT6906\\\">\\r\\n<p>View Pricing<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-section\\\" id=\\\"SECTION5622\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-section-background\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-container\\\">\\r\\n<div cla