Holding positions<br \\/>\\r\\nBurping techniques<br \\/>\\r\\nBurping pressure<br \\/>\\r\\nTiming of burping<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH7054\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">Purposes:<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH7055\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">Reducing spit-up and aiding in more efficient feeding<br \\/>\\r\\nEffective burping helps alleviate discomfort from gas and bloating, reducing episodes of crying<br \\/>\\r\\nSupporting the easier transition to sleep and better quality sleep<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7083\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7084\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7085\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7086\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7087\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7088\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"SHAPE7089\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-shape\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"GROUP6989\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-group\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"IMAGE6911\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-image\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-image-background\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-element\\\" id=\\\"PARAGRAPH7056\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ladi-paragraph\\\">3<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\