></div></div><div id=\"SECTION2283\" class=\'ladi-section\'><div class=\'ladi-section-background\'></div><div class=\"ladi-container\"><div id=\"IMAGE6894\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-image\'><div class=\"ladi-image-background\"></div></div></div><div id=\"IMAGE5653\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-image ladi-transition\'><div class=\"ladi-image-background\"></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6944\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"SHAPE6886\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6887\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6888\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6889\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6885\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Are you struggling to establish a healthy sleep routine for your newborn? <br>Spending countless hours trying to lull them to sleep? <br>Is your little one experiencing restless nights, with short 45-minute naps? <br>And amidst it all, are you longing for some precious moments of rest and rejuvenation? <br>Imagine having 7-8 hours of uninterrupted sleep each night, feeling refreshed and energized every morning with our course!<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6890\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6886\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>At <span style=\"color: rgb(45, 174, 235);\">POH Sleep</span>, we specialize in teaching newborns the invaluable skill of self-soothing and independent sleep. With our proven techniques, we have guided thousands of newborns aged 0-3 months to develop the ability to sleep on their own.<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6887\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 174, 235); font-weight: bold;\">And here\'s the best part: </span>It\'s never too early to start! In fact, the younger the baby, the more receptive they are to learning this essential skill. Our methods are gentle, tear-free, and highly effective, particularly for infants aged 0-4 weeks. We make self-sleeping a breeze, ensuring your baby drifts off peacefully, all on their own.<br></div></div><div id=\"VIDEO6891\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-video\'><div class=\"ladi-video-background\"></div><div id=\"SHAPE6891\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 408.7 408.7\" fill=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_FkQyXLSiVH\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div data-action=\"true\" id=\"BUTTON6905\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-button ladi-transition\'><div class=\"ladi-button-background\"></div><div id=\"BUTTON_TEXT6905\" class=\'ladi-element ladi-button-headline\'><p class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>View Pricing</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"SECTION6861\" class=\'ladi-section\'><div class=\'ladi-section-background\'></div><div class=\"ladi-container\"><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6890\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Your baby becomes more independent in their sleep routine, needing less assistance from you.\r\n<br>Best-case scenario: Your baby can sleep on their own with minimal or no support (usually less than 5 minutes).<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6893\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 263.4 150.6\" class=\"\" fill=\"url(\"#SHAPE6893_desktop_gradient\")\"><defs id=\"SHAPE6893_defs\"><linearGradient id=\"SHAPE6893_desktop_gradient\" gradientTransform=\"rotate(45)\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#2DAEEB\"></stop></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M146.3,150.6c-53.1,0-91.3-26.6-121-68.1C16.2,69.6,7.7,56.2,2.7,41-.5,31.4-2.2,21.6,5.6,14S25.3,3.8,36.9,6c8.4,1.5,15.4,6.3,22,11.4C78.6,32.9,100.8,40.5,126,40.1c19.4-.3,33.9-12.8,50.7-19.5,12.8-5.1,25-11.4,37.9-16.2,33.7-12.6,47,2.6,48.8,34.2,1.6,28-9.8,51.9-27.5,73C212.5,139.5,181.8,150.6,146.3,150.6Z\"></path></svg></div></div><div id=\"HEADLINE6888\" class=\'ladi-element\'><h3 class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>The Power of POH’s Sleep Training Courses</h3></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6888\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Unlock the incredible benefits of our sleep training course and watch your baby thrive:<br></div></div><div id=\"IMAGE6885\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-image ladi-transition\'><div class=\"ladi-image-background\"></div></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6891\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>IMPROVED NIGHT SLEEP<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6892\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Your baby\'s nighttime sleep becomes longer, minimizing disruptions during the day.\r\n<br>Best-case scenario: Your baby sleeps 10-12 hours at night, waking up for feeding only 1-3 times and falling back to sleep immediately. Once your baby weighs over 6kg, they can sleep through the night for 10-12 hours without needing to eat.<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6896\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6897\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6893\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>TIME FOR YOU TO REST & SELF-CARE<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6894\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>With your baby\'s improved sleep, you\'ll have valuable time to recharge and take care of yourself.\r\n<br>Relax and unwind, knowing your baby is peacefully sleeping.<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6898\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6899\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6889\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-para