id=\"BUTTON_TEXT6906\" class=\'ladi-element ladi-button-headline\'><p class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>View Pricing</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"SECTION5622\" class=\'ladi-section\'><div class=\'ladi-section-background\'></div><div class=\"ladi-container\"><div id=\"HEADLINE6889\" class=\'ladi-element\'><h3 class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>OCTA Method: Unlock Your Baby\'s Sleep Potential</h3></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6895\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>At POH’s Sleep Training Courses, we create the OCTA method that empowers newborns to self-soothe and establishes healthy sleep patterns. It consists of a daily routine that follows the sequence: Eat - Play - Sleep. This sequence is repeated throughout the day until bedtime, which creates a good foundation for night sleep.<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6896\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>This routine is designed to ensure efficient feeding by creating a more suitable daytime feeding schedule and optimizing energy storage.<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6897\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Contributing to better sleep quality</div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6899\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>=></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6902\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 174.8 150.1\" class=\"\" fill=\"url(\"#SHAPE6902_desktop_gradient\")\"><defs id=\"SHAPE6902_defs\"><linearGradient id=\"SHAPE6902_desktop_gradient\" gradientTransform=\"rotate(45)\"><stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"></stop><stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#2DAEEB\"></stop></linearGradient></defs><path d=\"M172,90.2a82.8,82.8,0,0,1-5.4,14.8,72.7,72.7,0,0,1-10.7,16.4,69.9,69.9,0,0,1-13.4,11.9c-9.7,6.6-22.2,11.7-38.2,14-36.1,5.1-55.9,3-69.8-3.6a63.5,63.5,0,0,1-17.5-12.7C-28.8,86.1,31.5,6