Reducing spit-up and aiding in more efficient feeding<br>Effective burping helps alleviate discomfort from gas and bloating, reducing episodes of crying<br>Supporting the easier transition to sleep and better quality sleep<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7083\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7084\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7085\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7086\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7087\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7088\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7089\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6989\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"IMAGE6911\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-image\'><div class=\"ladi-image-background\"></div></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7056\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>3<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7057\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Daily Routine<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7058\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>The daily routine for your child follows the rule of \"Eat-Play-Sleep.\" It means that when your baby wakes up, they will be fed when hungry, followed by playtime, and then put to sleep when they show signs of tiredness. This routine is repeated throughout the day until bedtime.<br>The timing of feeding, wakefulness, and sleep for each baby at different stages varies and depends entirely on their individual needs. By observing signals such as hunger and sleepiness, parents can accurately meet their child\'s needs.<br>A baby who follows a suitable daily routine will feel full, get enough sleep, and have longer nighttime sleep. When their needs are met accurately, they will be happy and smiling.<br>Along with a suitable daily routine, when a baby reaches a weight of 6-7kg, they are ready to store enough energy during the day and can sleep through the night for 10-12 hours without feeding.<br>This is also the time when parents can enjoy a full night\'s rest without interruptions.<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7090\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7091\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7092\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7093\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7094\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6990\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"IMAGE6912\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-image\'><div class=\"ladi-image-background\"></div></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7059\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>4<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7060\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Bedtime Routine for Newborns<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7061\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>A newborn can learn to put themselves to sleep if the OCTA sequence steps are followed consistently, along with ensuring the following factors:<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7062\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Having a consistent bedtime routine and appropriate sleep aids.\r\n<br>Providing support from parents at the crib or bassinet.\r\n<br>Creating a safe and sleep-friendly environment with a cool temperature and a dark room<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH7063\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>At POH Baby, we have successfully supported thousands of newborns in learning how to self-soothe and sleep. We have found that the easiest and most convenient stage to help babies learn to self-sleep without shedding a single tear is the 0-4 week age range.<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7095\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7096\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7097\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 1280 1896.08\" class=\"\" fill=\"#2DAEEB\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_uYaxlIaBRp\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"SECTION6720\" class=\'ladi-section\'><div class=\'ladi-section-background\'></div><div class=\"ladi-container\"><div data-action=\"true\" id=\"BUTTON6894\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-button ladi-transition\'><div class=\"ladi-button-background\"></div><div id=\"BUTTON_TEXT6894\" class=\'ladi-element ladi-button-headline\'><p class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>View Pricing</p></div></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE6937\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org