/svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7015\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6930\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Easy and convenient learning on the POH App<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6931\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Access course materials effortlessly through the user-friendly POH app<br>Study and review the content whenever and wherever it\'s convenient for you<br>Seamlessly integrate learning into your daily routine<br></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6992\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6924\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Six-Month course activation period<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6925\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Enjoy access to course materials for a generous six-month period<br>Learn at your own pace and revisit the content whenever needed<br>No rush or pressure—take your time to absorb the valuable information<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7022\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7023\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7024\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6932\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Experience the flexibility and cost-saving benefits of our online course package. Start your journey towards better sleep for your child and yourself today.<br></div></div></div></div><div id=\"SECTION5784\" class=\'ladi-section\'><div class=\'ladi-section-background\'></div><div class=\"ladi-container\"><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6944\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Experience the peace of mind that comes with personalized support tailored to your unique needs. Take advantage of our 1-on-1 consultation package and ensure both you and your little one achieve the desired results.<br></div></div><div id=\"HEADLINE6891\" class=\'ladi-element\'><h3 class=\'ladi-headline ladi-transition\'>Accelerate Your Child\'s Successful Self-Sleeping with Personalized 1-1 Consultation</h3></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6936\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Our personalized 1-1 sleep training consultant service is designed to expedite your child\'s journey towards independent sleep, ensuring both their well-being and your own. Benefit from our extensive expertise and optimized counseling techniques, derived from counseling nearly 20,000 babies using a healthy Routine since 2018.<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6937\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Here\'s how our 1-1 sleep consultant service works:<br></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6999\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6942\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Cost-effective solution<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6943\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Enjoy all the benefits of personalized 1-on-1 support at an extremely reasonable cost.\r\n<br>The price of one week of 1-on-1 monitoring is equivalent to a single phone call session.\r\n<br>It\'s a cost-effective investment in your child\'s sleep and your own well-being<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7025\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7026\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7027\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6998\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6940\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Convenience and flexibility<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6941\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Ask questions at any time, without scheduling separate appointments.\r\n<br>Eliminate worries about scheduling conflicts or interruptions during video calls.\r\n<br>We\'re here to support you whenever you need us<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7028\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7029\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7030\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6997\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-group\'><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6938\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Tailored support for your needs<br></div></div><div id=\"PARAGRAPH6939\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-paragraph\'>Receive daily monitoring and prompt assistance with any issues you encounter<br>No waiting for scheduled appointments or accumulating questions<br>Address concerns immediately, even if it\'s just a single question<br></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7031\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7032\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div><div id=\"SHAPE7033\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'ladi-shape\'><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 960 960\" width=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"\" fill=\"rgba(45, 174, 235, 1)\"><use xlink:href=\"#shape_gyrpaBgiOr\"></use></svg></div></div></div></div><div id=\"GROUP6996\" class=\'ladi-element\'><div class=\'la